originalText.text: Owen is amazing. I love this spa. They have great service. I didn't make an appointment this time because I was in a hurry. They accommodated me. It was a 90-minute body massage experience. I felt good. I would recommend them to you as well.

originalText.text:
Love this spa! Usually can accommodate walkins, service has always been great, appointments start right on time + you cannot beat the price! Great value for money.

I like to do their foot and body massage combo. Regardless of which treatment you opt for, they always finish with hot stones which is such a nice touch and elevates the overall experience!

originalText.text: I came here yesterday afternoon to relax my body. The male masseuse who began to massage for me was very skillful. He helped me massage my neck and shoulders comfortably, but I don't know why. More than ten minutes later, another male masseuse came in to give me a massage. Oh, my God, he simply couldn't massage and pressed my waist and legs very hard. It can be said that he can't massage. The owner of this massage parlor is simply cheating!

originalText.text: Please read beyond the 5-star reviews. This was an overall horrible experience. After a 90 minute full body massage, you should leave feeling relaxed not worse than before. If you’re into extra deep tissue, these folks might be your cup of tea. Otherwise, it’s a no. Masseurs do not speak English. They’re extremely rough. And the overall facility was less than mediocre. Even inexpensive spas outshine this. Do not fall into the TikTok trap, especially if you’ve had a massage before. The 2 stars is only because the people were nice.

originalText.text: I did a 90-minute massage here today, I think it was a painful experience both for me and for the masseur. The male masseur who gave me a massage not only did not speak English, but also was assigned to work as if he had just started to learn massage. He did same several movements over and over again, which made me very uncomfortable. The cashier also asked me, "Do you feel good?" How can she not know? Such services must be exposed!
